{
  "texts": [
    "For the video-gloss part, we align glosses with their corresponding videos based on their annotations (which are often the glosses themselves).",
    "By using glosses as an intermediary bridge between video and text, we have simplified an otherwise complex mapping network, thereby substantially reducing the number of connections in our database.",
    "This dual-mapping approach in our database ensures comprehensive coverage and flexibility in translation.",
    "It allows users to not only see the direct translation of a word into Auslan but also understand the different ways a concept can be expressed in Auslan.As shown in Fig. 1, in the function of text-to-sign lookup, users are expected to type in text strings into the input text box.",
    "Our lookup system initially searches the text in our database to find a matched word or phrase."
  ]
}